The paper deals with online boosting, a machine learning technique, which is a subfield of both machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The algorithms developed in the paper involve online loss minimization, which is a common technique in data structures (cs.DS). The paper also includes an extensive experimental study, which suggests that it may be relevant to computer vision (cs.CV) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
